name: DO NOT INSERT INSIDE THE EAR CANAL!!!
name_original: DO NOT INSERT INSIDE THE EAR CANAL!!!
description:
Clean out the inside of your ears **BY DISREGARDING THE EXPLICIT INSTRUCTIONS AGAINST USING COTTON SWABS FOR THIS PURPOSE** written on the package of the cotton swabs.

## CONTROLS

* Space to do something

* Click or touch does the same thing as space (in case you're on mobile I guess)

**Made in 4 hours on Sunday** because I was doing other stuff and Friday and Saturday.

Graphics with GIMP.

Built with Phaser 3 and Typescript.

SFX by my face.

Music generated with help from WolframTones.

Source linked.

## Be gentle, it's a compo game!
